content.rendered:
Directed by Nilesh Sahay

Written by Shobha Nihalani. Nilesh Sahay

Star Mohan Kapur (Abhay Bhatnagar). Pooja Batra (Nandini Rajput). Malvika Raaj (Aaria). Rinzing Denzongpa (Bhim). Ajit Shidhaye (Razak (credit only)). Ashish Tyagi (Girish). Abdullah Osman (Aayutam). Tanisha Dhillon (Addy). Amit Gaur (Ajay). Dishita Jain (Mimi). Rohan Arora (Nakul). Vinayak Dubey (Arjun). Aman Varma (Bomb Expert)

Language Hindi

Producers Mohan Gopinath . Manish Pandya. Nilesh Sahay. Brajesh Sahaya

Production IMEN. Indian Media Entertainment Network
